xfce4-applemenu-plugin (0.3.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Fixed deprecated GTK+ API calls for GTK3 compatibility
  * Fixed format security warnings in error dialogs
  * Added multiarch support for plugin installation
  * Fixed desktop file with proper Name and Comment fields
  * Improved Debian packaging rules for Meson builds
  * Removed obsolete intltool dependencies
  * Added universal install script with distribution detection

 -- Kamil "Novik" Nowicki <novik@axisos.org>  Wed, 23 Jan 2025 12:00:00 +0100

xfce4-applemenu-plugin (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release
  * Fixed menu toggle issue on second click
  * Migrated build system from Autotools to Meson
  * Added Debian 11 compatibility

